dct_description_sm: Oriented with north to the right.
Includes 3 insets : Fukin ippanzu; Kōbe Aakashi kan zu; Akashi shigaizu.
Text, pictures and index of streets' names and two maps (Banshū chizu and Himeji-shi zenzu) on verso.
